insect.coverage.instrumentation
Class Instrumentor

java.lang.Object
  insect.coverage.instrumentation.Instrumentor
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.apache.bcel.Constants
public class Instrumentor
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.bcel.Constants

Instruments a set of classes specified in a resource file with a number of different probes. The classes are first copied and the instrumentation is performed on those copies. The actual instrumentation process is delegated to the ProbeInserter class.

Author:
Anil Chawla
